{"tid":2142833,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"記協稱警方不就有人涉教唆他人偽造記者證採取檢控行動","createTime":"2020-08-06T16:39:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T19:20:51.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e4c7a39141ed5c19108e8522db50ad7985fa5523","tid":2142833,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:39:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542271-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542271-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=il%2BrReVPph3FBkDtfLAFOllsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=7e2386ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542271-20200806.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6394fe55\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542271-20200806.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會今年5月報案，表示有人在名為「李力持」的社交網頁，上載記協的記者證樣本，涉嫌教唆他人偽造記者證。警方日前回覆記協，表示證據不足，不會就案件採取檢控行動。<br />\n<br />\n記協主席楊健興下午去信警務處處長鄧炳強，表達不滿，同時對警方沒有正面回應記協提問，感到遺憾及失望，促請警方詳細回答對案件的查詢，再次展開深入調查。<br />\n<br />\n楊健興在信中表示，記協記者證是警方承認的證件，有人公開在社交平台張貼證件式樣，並鼓勵公眾自製證件，警方理應不希望出現有關混亂情況，但處理案件的態度令人感到警方不著緊證件真偽的問題，又指警方過去一年多不斷提及有「假記者」、「假證件」等，但針對相關案件，卻沒有有人被檢控或需要承擔後果。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，警方有責任調查刑事罪行，即使證據不足亦應該向公眾作出交代，並提醒公眾切勿以身試法，否則將會向社會傳遞錯誤信息，甚至構建這類網上鼓勵他人偽造證件的行為，毋需承擔法律責任的虛假印象。"},{"pid":"df775103442c7d64675c0f71e25dc24d45ca8f1b","tid":2142833,"uid":127929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:47:49.000Z","msg":"因為警察有份指使，正如警察有份配合721元朗白衣黑社會恐襲一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74396f7f3c8976f7276c478aea75231b4f337246","tid":2142833,"uid":160102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:52:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bef304ee518b621687897346ebd0debdd6f61a41","tid":2142833,"uid":63543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T16:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3b945a4d5ebffbafc719d122f6de07efa137610","tid":2142833,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T18:34:37.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be634acdeca57ead9e69c83a5b8aeb6d9b4b89e","tid":2142833,"uid":20025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-06T19:20:51.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}